PIA's Boeing 720-B. This big, comfortable plane
leaves Karachi every Tuesday at 9 A.M. and every
thurscay at layr.m. On the way. in addition
to its now famous service PIA provides cinema on
board to both Economy and First Class passengers.
PIA is the only airline that does this. If you are
